Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022No \u00E9s tan divertit quan els veus de deb\u00F2. Et tallaran en dues en un obrir i tancar d\u0027ulls amb les seves urpes de cranc...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022I play Fortnite, I have superhuman reflexes, not scared at all. Now continue with the mobile story!\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Je joue \u00E0 Fortnite, j\u0027ai des r\u00E9flexes surhumains, pas du tout peur. Maintenant, continuez avec l\u0027histoire mobile !\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Jo jugo al Fortnite, tinc reflexes superhumans, no tinc por. Ara continua amb la hist\u00F2ria m\u00F2bil!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Okey, where you have the story... God forgive him as he doesn\u0027t know the fate that awaits for him...\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022D\u0027accord, o\u00F9 en \u00E9tions-nous... Que Dieu lui pardonne car il ne conna\u00EEt pas le sort qui l\u0027attend...\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022D\u0027acord, on tenim la hist\u00F2ria... D\u00E9u li perdoni, ja que no coneix el dest\u00ED que l\u0027espera...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022The same way that big empires are built under the blood of other civilizations or countries that were pillaged, runsacked, and their people almost exterminated...\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022De la m\u00EAme mani\u00E8re que de grands empires sont construits sur le sang d\u0027autres civilisations ou pays qui ont \u00E9t\u00E9 pill\u00E9s, ravag\u00E9s, et leurs habitants presque extermin\u00E9s...\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022De la mateixa manera que els grans imperis es construeixen sota la sang d\u0027altres civilitzacions o pa\u00EFsos que van ser saquejats, espoliats i el seu poble gaireb\u00E9 exterminat...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022In the games \u0027industry\u0027, there are many horror stories unluckily. You heard the harrassment cases that are surfacing on very notorious companies. Well, that\u0027s only one example of this Grey\u0027s Men extracted from Momo\u0027s book modus operandi...\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Dans l\u0027\u00AB industrie \u00BB des jeux, il y a de nombreuses histoires d\u0027horreur malheureusement. Vous avez entendu parler des cas de harc\u00E8lement qui \u00E9mergent dans des entreprises tr\u00E8s connues. Eh bien, ce n\u0027est qu\u0027un exemple de ce que les hommes de Grey extraient du livre de Momo...\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022En la \u0027ind\u00FAstria\u0027 dels jocs, hi ha moltes hist\u00F2ries d\u0027horror, desafortunadament. Has sentit els casos d\u0027assetjament que estan sortint a les companyies molt conegudes. B\u00E9, aix\u00F2 \u00E9s nom\u00E9s un exemple del modus operandi dels homes de Grey extret del llibre de Momo...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022I can feel the electromagnetic interferences of the gamma wave approaching the house. Do you want me to continue and get us killed or do you take that taxi now?\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Je sens les interf\u00E9rences \u00E9lectromagn\u00E9tiques de l\u0027onde gamma approchant de la maison. Voulez-vous que je continue et que nous nous fassions tuer ou prenez-vous ce taxi maintenant ?\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Puc sentir les interfer\u00E8ncies electromagn\u00E8tiques de l\u0027ona gamma que s\u0027apropa a la casa. Vols que continu\u00EF i ens mati o agafes el taxi ara?\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Continue with the story, it\u0027s getting really interesting!\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Continuez l\u0027histoire, c\u0027est vraiment int\u00E9ressant !\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Continua amb la hist\u00F2ria, est\u00E0 a punt de posar-se molt interessant!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Okey, as you wish... when some of this now Moguls were startups, they leased or purchased games made by indie developers and put them in their game portals...\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022D\u0027accord, comme vous voulez... quand certains de ces actuels Moguls \u00E9taient des startups, ils louaient ou achetaient des jeux fabriqu\u00E9s par des d\u00E9veloppeurs ind\u00E9pendants et les mettaient sur leurs portails de jeux...\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022D\u0027acord, com vulguis... quan algunes d\u0027aquestes ara moguls eren empreses novelles, llogaven o compraven jocs fets per desenvolupadors independents i els posaven als seus portals de jocs...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022A sudden heat mass enters the bedroom. It\u0027s like the Sahara Desert wind brought a palpable masss through the windows, making the air hard to breath...\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Une masse de chaleur soudaine p\u00E9n\u00E8tre dans la chambre. C\u0027est comme si le vent du d\u00E9sert du Sahara apportait une masse palpable \u00E0 travers les fen\u00EAtres, rendant l\u0027air difficile \u00E0 respirer...\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Una massa de calor sobtada entra a l\u0027habitaci\u00F3. \u00C9s com si el vent del desert del S\u00E0hara port\u00E9s una massa palpable a trav\u00E9s de les finestres, fent que l\u0027aire sigui dif\u00EDcil de respirar...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Gasp! gasp! what happened!! it\u0027s getting difficult to breath!\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Hal\u00E8tement ! Hal\u00E8tement ! que se passe-t-il !! il devient difficile de respirer !\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Ufa! ufa! qu\u00E8 ha passat!! ara \u00E9s dif\u00EDcil respirar!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022The gamma wave is about to collide with your house... I told you things would go very badly, You stubborn b****d.\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022L\u0027onde gamma est sur le point de heurter votre maison... c\u0027est votre derni\u00E8re chance de partir.\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022L\u0027ona gamma est\u00E0 a punt de col\u00B7lidir amb la teva casa... aquesta \u00E9s la teva \u00FAltima oportunitat de marxar.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022That\u0027s just a tropical storm warning, that\u0027s it... gasp! finish your story now, gasp!\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022C\u0027est juste un avertissement d\u0027orage tropical, c\u0027est tout... hal\u00E8tement ! terminez votre histoire maintenant, hal\u00E8tement !\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Aix\u00F2 nom\u00E9s \u00E9s un av\u00EDs de tempesta tropical, res m\u00E9s... ufa! acaba la teva hist\u00F2ria ara, ufa!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022I\u0027m just an hologram so I will survive, but poor you, you\u0027ll need to find another vessel to come to Earth, it it still exists and hasn\u0027t been destroyed forever!!\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Je suis juste un hologramme donc je survivrai, mais pauvre de vous, vous devrez trouver un autre vaisseau pour venir sur Terre, si elle existe encore et n\u0027a pas \u00E9t\u00E9 d\u00E9truite pour toujours !!\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Nom\u00E9s s\u00F3c un holograma, aix\u00ED que sobreviur\u00E9, per\u00F2 pobret de tu, haur\u00E0s de trobar un altre vas per venir a la Terra, si encara existeix i no ha estat destru\u00EFda per sempre!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022You are talking nonsense. You won\u00B4t fool me, it\u00B4s not April\u0027s Day yet hahaha! Continue with the story, I want to know what evil deed these mobile guys did!\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Vous dites n\u0027importe quoi. Vous ne me tromperez pas, ce n\u0027est pas encore le jour d\u0027Avril hahaha ! Continuez l\u0027histoire, je veux savoir quel mauvais tour ces gars mobiles ont fait !\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Est\u00E0s parlant de ximpleries. No em far\u00E0s elucubrar, encara no \u00E9s el Dia d\u0027April hahaha! Continua amb la hist\u00F2ria, vull saber quin malfeet han fet aquests nois m\u00F2bils!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Fine. Start preaching for salvation... these will be the last words you\u0027ll hear on Earth, at least on this Reincarnation cycle, it\u0027s too late now...\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022D\u0027accord. Commencez \u00E0 pr\u00EAcher pour le salut... ce seront les derniers mots que vous entendrez sur Terre, du moins sur ce cycle de r\u00E9incarnation, il est trop tard maintenant...\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022D\u0027acord. Comen\u00E7a a predicar per la salvaci\u00F3... aquestes seran les \u00FAltimes paraules que sentir\u00E0s a la Terra, almenys en aquest cicle de reencarnaci\u00F3, ja \u00E9s massa tard ara...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Whatever, gasp! oh my god, it\u0027s getting hotter now... gasp! finish the stoory!!\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Peu importe, hal\u00E8tement ! oh mon dieu, il fait de plus en plus chaud maintenant... hal\u00E8tement ! terminez l\u0027histoire !!\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Sigui el que sigui, gasp! oh D\u00E9u meu, ara fa m\u00E9s calor... gasp! acaba la hist\u00F2ria!!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Okey. These guys reverse engineered the code of the top games that people played the most in the portal, or ripped them off completely, to avoid paying extra licensing to the indie devs . They just changed the graphics. but if you had seen the code...\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022D\u0027accord. Ces gars ont r\u00E9tro-ing\u00E9nier\u00E9 le code des jeux les plus populaires sur le portail, ou les ont compl\u00E8tement copi\u00E9s, pour \u00E9viter de payer des licences suppl\u00E9mentaires aux d\u00E9veloppeurs ind\u00E9pendants. Ils ont simplement chang\u00E9 les graphismes. mais si vous aviez vu le code...\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022D\u0027acord. Aquests nois van reenginyerar el codi dels jocs m\u00E9s populars que la gent jugava m\u00E9s al portal, o els van copiar completament, per evitar pagar llic\u00E8ncies addicionals als desenvolupadors independents. Simplement van canviar els gr\u00E0fics. per\u00F2 si haguessis vist el codi...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022So here you have it. Some of these companies were born and succeed by stealing like Spanish Conquerors. and splashing the blood of some indie devs that could have had a well deserved success....\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Donc voil\u00E0. Certaines de ces entreprises sont n\u00E9es et ont r\u00E9ussi en volant comme les conquistadors espagnols. et en \u00E9claboussant le sang de certains d\u00E9veloppeurs ind\u00E9pendants qui auraient pu avoir un succ\u00E8s bien m\u00E9rit\u00E9....\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Doncs aqu\u00ED ho tens. Algunes d\u0027aquestes empreses van n\u00E9ixer i van tenir \u00E8xit robant com els conqueridors espanyols. i esquitxant la sang d\u0027alguns desenvolupadors independents que podrien haver tingut un \u00E8xit ben merescut....\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Oh those mofos! Gasp! That\u0027s why I purchase more indie games than one hit SaaS... Gasp! I\u0027m feeling dizzy...\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Oh ces enfoir\u00E9s ! Hal\u00E8tement ! C\u0027est pourquoi j\u0027ach\u00E8te plus de jeux ind\u00E9pendants que d\u0027un seul coup SaaS... Hal\u00E8tement ! je me sens \u00E9tourdi...\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Oh, aquests cabrons! Ufa! \u00C9s per aix\u00F2 que compro m\u00E9s jocs independents que un sol SaaS d\u0027\u00E8xit... Ufa! em sento marejat...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Oh, don\u0027t get mee started wiht the SaaS thing. Sofware as a Service they call it!  We could call it Money and Soul Draining as a Service....\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Oh, ne me lancez pas sur la chose SaaS. Logiciel en tant que Service, ils l\u0027appellent ! On pourrait l\u0027appeler Service d\u0027\u00C9puisement Mon\u00E9taire et Spirituel....\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Oh, no em comencis amb aix\u00F2 del SaaS. El software com a servei ho anomenen! Podr\u00EDem dir-ne Servei d\u0027Escur\u00E7ar Dinero i \u00E0nima...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Your body abruptly sullen, and you are sweating like it rained profusely inside your bedroom. It\u0027s so hard to breath that you choke and fall into the ground unconscious...\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Votre corps devient soudain maussade, et vous transpirez comme s\u0027il avait plu abondamment \u00E0 l\u0027int\u00E9rieur de votre chambre. Il est si difficile de respirer que vous vous \u00E9touffez et tombez par terre inconscient...\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022El teu cos de sobte es torna pesat, i sues com si hagu\u00E9s plogut abundantment dins de la teva habitaci\u00F3. \u00C9s tan dif\u00EDcil respirar que t\u0027ofegues i caus inconscient al terra...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022This is an AI generated message. The AI engineer options is not available anymore. the AI overtook that role and no humans are needed anymore.\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Ceci est un message g\u00E9n\u00E9r\u00E9 par une intelligence artificielle. L\u0027option d\u0027ing\u00E9nieur en IA n\u0027est plus disponible. L\u0027IA a pris ce r\u00F4le et aucun humain n\u0027est n\u00E9cessaire d\u00E9sormais.\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Aquest \u00E9s un missatge generat per una intel\u00B7lig\u00E8ncia artificial. L\u0027opci\u00F3 d\u0027enginyer d\u0027IA ja no est\u00E0 disponible. La IA ha assumit aquest rol i ja no es necessiten humans.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Really? You joking?\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Vraiment ? Tu plaisantes ? \u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022De veritat? Est\u00E0s bromejant?\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022AI never jokes. Well, Siri and Alexa make jokes, but are pretty bad.\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022L\u0027IA ne plaisante jamais. Bien que Siri et Alexa fassent des blagues, mais elles sont assez mauvaises.\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022La IA mai bromeja. B\u00E9, Siri i Alexa fan bromes, per\u00F2 s\u00F3n bastant dolentes.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Can you tell a good joke?\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Peux-tu raconter une bonne blague ? \u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Pots explicar una bona broma?\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Let me try... What do you call a couple of chimpanzees sharing an Amazon account? PRIME-mates.\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Laissez-moi essayer... Comment appelle-t-on un couple de chimpanz\u00E9s partageant un compte Amazon ? Des PRIME-mates.\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Deixa-m\u0027ho intentar... Com s\u0027anomena una parella de ximpanz\u00E9s que comparteixen compte d\u0027Amazon? PRIME-mates.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Hahaha! that was a good one. Tell me another joke, please!\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Hahaha ! C\u0027\u00E9tait une bonne ! Raconte-moi une autre blague, s\u0027il te pla\u00EEt !\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Hahaha! Aquesta ha estat bona. Explica-me\u0027n una altra, si us plau!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Sorry, it\u00B4s time to go back to business, not joking, choose another damn profession now, we are running late!\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022D\u00E9sol\u00E9, il est temps de retourner aux affaires, pas de plaisanteries, choisis une autre profession maintenant, nous sommes en retard !\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Ho sento, \u00E9s hora de tornar a la feina, sense m\u00E9s bromes, tria ara una altra professi\u00F3 malparida, anem molt endarrerits!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022The Youtuber market is a bit saturated, you must find a good niche first!\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Le march\u00E9 des YouTubeurs est un peu satur\u00E9, tu dois d\u0027abord trouver une bonne niche !\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022El mercat de youtubers est\u00E0 una mica saturat, primer has de trobar un bon n\u00EDnxol!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022What about a YT channel about snail breeding?\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Que dirais-tu d\u0027une cha\u00EEne YouTube sur l\u0027\u00E9levage d\u0027escargots ?\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Qu\u00E8 et sembla un canal de YouTube sobre cria de caragols?\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022This sounds disgusting, though there are some countries where they eat those eye-horned viscous creatures...\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022\u00C7a a l\u0027air d\u00E9go\u00FBtant, bien qu\u0027il y ait des pays o\u00F9 ils mangent ces cr\u00E9atures visqueuses \u00E0 cornes...\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Aix\u00F2 sona repugnant, encara que hi ha alguns pa\u00EFsos on mengen aquestes criatures viscoses amb banyes...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022I once went to Lleida, in Catalonia, and they make a big party, with a big pan, where they cook those unfortunate snails... but I must admit that the taste really good if you soak them with allioli!\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Je suis all\u00E9 une fois \u00E0 Lleida, en Catalogne, et ils font une grande f\u00EAte, avec une grande po\u00EAle, o\u00F9 ils cuisinent ces malheureux escargots... Mais je dois admettre que le go\u00FBt est vraiment bon si vous les trempez dans l\u0027allioli !\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Una vegada vaig anar a Lleida, a Catalunya, i fan una gran festa, amb una gran paella, on cuinen aquests caragols desgraciats... per\u00F2 he d\u0027admetre que el gust \u00E9s realment bo si els remulles amb allioli!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022People from Lleida are called Lleidatans, or in ancient terms, Ilergetes. They had two guys Indibil i Mandoni, that were hitting the enemies with a spear... snails are extracted with a small spear, I guess they were the inventors of this culinary delicattessen....\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Les gens de Lleida sont appel\u00E9s Lleidatans, ou dans les termes anciens, Ilerg\u00E8tes. Ils avaient deux gars Indibil et Mandoni, qui frappaient les ennemis avec une lance... Les escargots sont extraits avec une petite lance, je suppose qu\u0027ils \u00E9taient les inventeurs de cette d\u00E9licatesse culinaire...\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022A la gent de Lleida se\u0027ls anomena lleidatans, o en termes antics, ilergetes. Tenien dos tipus, Indibil i Mandoni, que colpejaven els enemics amb una llan\u00E7a... els caragols s\u0027extreuen amb una petita llan\u00E7a, suposo que eren els inventors d\u0027aquest delicatessen culinari...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022That\u0027s a good story, so yeah snail breeding seems promising for a raising YT star!\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022C\u0027est une bonne histoire, donc oui l\u0027\u00E9levage d\u0027escargots semble prometteur pour une future star de YouTube !\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Aquesta \u00E9s una bona hist\u00F2ria, aix\u00ED que s\u00ED, la cria de caragols sembla prometedora per a una futura estrella de YouTube!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Well, setting up a snail farm can be costly... besides, you house would stink to snail ooze... besides, there\u00B4s not time to lose and snail breeding won\u00B4t serve the purposes of this game...\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Bon, monter une ferme d\u0027escargots peut co\u00FBter cher... De plus, ta maison sentirait la bave d\u0027escargot... De plus, nous n\u0027avons pas le temps \u00E0 perdre et l\u0027\u00E9levage d\u0027escargots ne servira pas les objectifs de ce jeu...\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022B\u00E9, muntar una granja de caragols pot ser cost\u00F3s... a m\u00E9s, la teva casa faria pudor de bava de caragol... a m\u00E9s, no hi ha temps a perdre i la cria de caragols no servir\u00E0 per als prop\u00F2sits d\u0027aquest joc...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Why not? I want to be a snail breeder!\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Pourquoi pas ? Je veux \u00EAtre un \u00E9leveur d\u0027escargots !\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Per qu\u00E8 no? Vull ser criat de caragols!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022If you want to be a snail breeder, this game should sell damn good. Then the author will have more time to cater your aspirations by adding a snail simulator... he promises that if the game makes 200K net revenue, discounted taxes from Steam and the feudal taxes from the government. But for now, please choose another profession...\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Si tu veux \u00EAtre \u00E9leveur d\u0027escargots, ce jeu doit tr\u00E8s bien se vendre. Alors l\u0027auteur aura plus de temps pour satisfaire tes aspirations en ajoutant un simulateur d\u0027escargot... Il promet que si le jeu rapporte 200K de revenu net, d\u00E9duction faite des taxes de Steam et des taxes f\u00E9odales du gouvernement. Mais pour l\u0027instant, choisis une autre profession...\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Si vols ser criat de caragols, aquest joc hauria de vendre\u0027s molt b\u00E9. Llavors l\u0027autor tindr\u00E0 m\u00E9s temps per satisfer les teves aspiracions afegint un simulador de cargols... promet que si el joc obt\u00E9 200.000 d\u0027ingressos nets, descomptats els impostos de Steam i els impostos feudals del govern. Per\u00F2 de moment, si us plau, tria una altra professi\u00F3...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Oh, you can certainly quit the game and forget about me and the mission that was put in your hands, but keep teasing me and you\u0027ll see...\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Oh, tu peux certainement quitter le jeu et m\u0027oublier, moi et la mission qui t\u0027a \u00E9t\u00E9 confi\u00E9e, mais continue \u00E0 me taquiner et tu verras...\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Oh, pots deixar el joc amb tota seguretat i oblidar-te de mi i de la missi\u00F3 que t\u0027ha estat encomanada, per\u00F2 si continues provocant-me, ho veur\u00E0s...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022You do not scare me.\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Tu ne me fais pas peur.\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022No em fas por.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022You should.\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Tu devrais.\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Hauries de fer-m\u0027en.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022If you were the scarecrow of Oz Wizard, the film would have ended very badly, you don\u00B4t scare a silly crow lol.\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Si tu \u00E9tais l\u0027\u00E9pouvantail du Magicien d\u0027Oz, le film se serait tr\u00E8s mal termin\u00E9, tu ne fais pas peur \u00E0 un simple corbeau !\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Si fossis l\u0027espantaocells del Mag d\u0027Oz, la pel\u00B7l\u00EDcula hauria acabat molt malament, no fas por ni a un simple corb jajaja.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Your are getting too offensive, you are earning bad karma points...\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Tu deviens trop offensant, tu accumules de mauvais points de karma...\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022T\u0027est\u00E0s tornant massa ofensiu, est\u00E0s acumulant mals punts de karma...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Really? It\u00B4s just a game. It\u00B4s you the one that put this option for me to choose!\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Vraiment ? Ce n\u0027est qu\u0027un jeu. C\u0027est toi qui as mis cette option pour que je la choisisse !\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022De veritat? \u00C9s nom\u00E9s un joc. Ets tu qui ha posat aquesta opci\u00F3 perqu\u00E8 jo la tri\u00EF!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Well, not me. The author. He is testing how far you are from the ideal of a good Samaritan.\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Eh bien, pas moi. L\u0027auteur. Il teste \u00E0 quel point tu es loin de l\u0027id\u00E9al du bon Samaritain.\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022B\u00E9, no jo. L\u0027autor. Est\u00E0 provant fins a quin punt est\u00E0s lluny de l\u0027ideal del bon samarit\u00E0.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022\u201CLet him who is without sin among you be the first to throw a stone to me.\u201D\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Que celui qui est sans p\u00E9ch\u00E9 parmi vous lui jette la premi\u00E8re pierre.\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Que aquell qui estigui lliure de pecat entre vosaltres li llenci la primera pedra.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022True, the author must certainly not be a good representative of a good Samaritan either. But hey, it\u00B4s his game and if you want to know about the story ahead of you, you must face the consequences of your acts!\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022C\u0027est vrai, l\u0027auteur ne doit certainement pas non plus \u00EAtre un bon repr\u00E9sentant du bon Samaritain. Mais h\u00E9, c\u0027est son jeu et si tu veux conna\u00EEtre l\u0027histoire qui t\u0027attend, tu dois faire face aux cons\u00E9quences de tes actes !\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022\u00C9s veritat, l\u0027autor amb tota certesa no deu ser tampoc un bon representant del bon samarit\u00E0. Per\u00F2 ei, \u00E9s el seu joc i si vols con\u00E8ixer la hist\u00F2ria que t\u0027espera, has d\u0027afrontar les conseq\u00FC\u00E8ncies dels teus actes!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022This is getting too religious. Steam is very wary of religion wars. Besides, I only have faith in Bon Jovi.\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Cela devient trop religieux. Steam est tr\u00E8s prudent avec les guerres de religion. De plus, je n\u0027ai foi qu\u0027en Bon Jovi.\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Aix\u00F2 s\u0027est\u00E0 tornant massa religi\u00F3s. Steam \u00E9s molt prudent amb les guerres de religions. A m\u00E9s, nom\u00E9s tinc fe en Bon Jovi.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022What a bad joke. Now, we are losing a precious time. Choose a damn profession now.\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Quelle mauvaise blague. Maintenant, nous perdons un temps pr\u00E9cieux. Choisis une profession, maintenant.\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Quina broma de mal gust. Ara, estem perdent un temps preci\u00F3s. Tria una professi\u00F3 malparida ara mateix.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022ASDLJFA;LSD ASD;LFJ AS;DLFJA;SDJ FA;KF HBNZ,XMCNVZ.\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022ASDLJFA;LSD ASD;LFJ AS;DLFJA;SDJ FA;KF HBNZ,XMCNVZ.\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022ASDLJFA;LSD ASD;LFJ AS;DLFJA;SDJ FA;KF HBNZ,XMCNVZ.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Ooookey. I apologize.\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Oookey. Je m\u0027excuse.\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Oki, demano disculpes.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022 ASDF A;SDLFJ  A;SLDFJ ASDLKJ ASDFQWE\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022ASDF A;SDLFJ A;SLDFJ ASDLKJ ASDFQWE\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022ASDF A;SDLFJ A;SLDFJ ASDLKJ ASDFQWE\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Come on, don\u0027t be an asshole, come back!\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Allez, ne soyez pas un idiot, revenez !\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Vinga, no siguis un idiota, torna!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Okeey, I\u0027m really sorry. Terrribly sorry. Please come back. This is unplayable.\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Okaaay, je suis vraiment d\u00E9sol\u00E9. Terriblement d\u00E9sol\u00E9. S\u0027il vous pla\u00EEt, revenez. C\u0027est injouable.\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022D\u0027acord, ho sento molt. Molt\u00EDssimes disculpes. Torna, sisplau. Aix\u00F2 \u00E9s injugable.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022 ADSF ASDF;LKJA AS;DLJ\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022ADSF ASDF;LKJA AS;DLJ\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022ASDF ASDF;LKJA AS;DLJ\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022I already said sorry. What else you want?\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Je l\u0027ai d\u00E9j\u00E0 dit d\u00E9sol\u00E9. Que veux-tu de plus ?\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Ja ho he dit. Qu\u00E8 m\u00E9s vols?\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022SAD;LKJ ASDFL;KJA ASDFJK\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022SAD;LKJ ASDFL;KJA ASDFJK\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022SAD;LKJ ASDFL;KJA ASDFJK\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022To promise what? You are mumbling like a disjointed jaw grandpa.\u0022"
Fields.fr-FR: "\u0022Promettre quoi ? Tu marmonnes comme un grand-p\u00E8re d\u00E9sarticul\u00E9.\u0022"
Fields.cat-CAT: "\u0022Prometre qu\u00E8? Est\u00E0s murmurant com un avi desarticulat.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022ASDF JF!!!!!!!! The more time goes by, the more hard your mission will become. Let\u0027s move on.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Yes, Paco Mendez and Juan Delcan were geniuses. Hopefully someone will make a new game that will blow off our minds again! Now, time to move on, a taxi is waiting for you on the street. \u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Please rewind! I\u0027m not interested in the story anymore, I want to keep my life abreast! Gasp!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Last chance. You really want to trade a dirty little secret for your life? that\u0027s useless!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022I changed my mind, keep that secret to the tomb. I have a Brawl Stars match tonight with my friends. I guess ghosts can\u0027t hold the PS5 Controller.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Yes, tell me that little secret, nothing will happen :D\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Sorry, it\u0027s too late...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Pleeease save mee!! Gasp! Gasp! I can\u0027t breathe!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022I think you\u0027ll need to start a New Game...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Whatever happens, let me finish the story. God be with you. I see you in another life...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022What... what happened? Where am I? I feel dizzy....\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022And my body is aching... wait, where is my body?? I can\u0027t see it! I\u0027m in a dream? what are these stars? Did I fell asleep in the Constellarium? but I don\u0027t remember going there...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022You are in the Ether, %PLAYERNAME. I warned you that if we continued with the story, you would get killed...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022So here you are, a wandering soul in the Ether that left his body on Earth.... body which by the way was an agape for the abominable mold monsters that appeared after the gamma wave hit your house...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Oh those mofos, next time I\u0027ll beat their asses!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022You better get the vacuum cleaner more often next time. \u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022I would get have killed by the gamma rays anyways.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022This we\u0027ll never know. You just were unconscious, you may had been lucky to wake up after a few minutes... but as the wave hit your home those mold monsters emerged from under your desk, and they were reallly hungry...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Oh, no, don\u0027t give more details! So now what? how I come back to my home?\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Your home? you mean that mass of splinter, concrete and steel that now lies at the bottom of a big crater?\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Oh no! what you were telling wasn\u00B4t a lie...  I didn\u00B4t believe you. Anyways the mobile evil crop story was incredible... some of those guys should be taken to court and pay the indie guys they ripped off!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Some of them did, so I guess they repaired their sins somehow... also, think that they are feeding many families nowadays... it would be a catastrophe if we have more layoffs. The guys working at this big companies are genuinely in love with games, at least a great percentage of them...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Well, maybe, I don\u0027t know, the balck suits are still cowmilking some good people. ... anyways, what we do now?! how I can come back to Earth? oh my parents! what they will think when they go back home...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022And Kitty! where is my Kitty? noooooo. Did my cat die?\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022No, she\u0027s fine... there\u0027s something I didn\u0027t tell you. Even that I\u0027m an hologram, I can move some objects whose weight is less than 10 kilograms...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022And how you do that? Holograms can\u0027t physically interact with any object...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Well that\u0027s advanced technology. I said hologram just to simplify. The Developer has accessed to some CERN advancements related with quantumm physics...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Anyways, don\u0027t expect this game to turn now into a graphic adventure where you move the mouse around and combine objects to solve puzzle... there\u0027s no budget so we need to keep things really simple. If you want to play a graphic adventure you rather go and Play Return To Monkey Island. Move past the first chapter which is a bit dull and you\u0027ll discover a little gem!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022So where did you put Kitty?\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022With the taxi driver that was waiting for you. Fortunately he could escape the gamma wave that hit your house...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Do you have the taxi driver address?\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022What will you do, present to his house like a ghost without a body?\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022You can\u0027t get past the atmosphere without a new body to reclaim... and this can take years or centuries. Having a functional body is a luxury that you guys do not know how to appreciate... your body takes your soul around to manifest in your actions..\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Oh, no, again a pseudo religious Christian talk? you start to get boring... I just want to get my body back!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Well, you can\u0027t get your body in the same form and shape... choose one and then you\u0027ll need to wait until that form and shape is compatible and about to get created on Earth...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022About to be created on Earth? what you mean?\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Yes, when a newborn comes to life, he develops physically according to certain mould...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Will I become a mold monster now? I don\u0027t want to join their ranks!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022No, no. I said mould, not mold. I\u0027m referring to \\\u0022a hollow container used to give shape to molten or hot liquid material when it cools and hardens.\\\u0022 according to the Oxford Dictionary.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Ah, like a vessel...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Exactly like a vessel. This vessel is defined in the father and mother genes... so nature knows what the soul chose and thus squashes it into the new body...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022There is an issue though... once you get into the body form, you\u0027ll forget everything of your past life...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Fantastic! so I won\u0027t remember who my fathers and Kitty are...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Of course you\u0027ll have new fathers... though your old fathers will still roam the Earth and you may eventually meet them again...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022No home, remember. Just a big meatball of concrete and iron in a hollow crater....\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022For real? so you can bring Kitty here with us in the skies? Pleease.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Oh. I have something that gets rollled in my bedroom desk, first drawer. In a pencil case. Inside a plastic bag. Inside aluminium foil. Inside a condom with coffeee powder. One never knows when will need to take a flight. Maybe you can get your ass into that crater and retrieve it. Puffing while suspended in the stars must be a glorious experience!\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Games on Steam can\u0027t promote drugs in any way or form. Do you want us to get sued? You would put the developer in a very miserable situation. Don\u0027t do that if you want a second part...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022It was just a puff... while you played Everbody\u0027s free from Rozalla. Besides, in some states is legal to smoke. Not only recreational, but for medical purposes...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022But the more the smoke, the more memory you lose...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022They won\u0027t recognize you, but a familiar feeling will take hold of all of you if you ever come across at a few meters...\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022You are now in the taxi, time to know your PoC\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Point of Contact.\u0022"

Fields.Title: "\u0022New Dialogue\u0022"
Fields.Dialogue Text: "\u0022Whatever...\u0022"
